<div class="container mt-3 mb-5 small">
    <h1 class="mb-4 fs-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. We are committed to protecting your personal data and being transparent about how we handle it.</p>

    <h3 class="small">1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and login credentials. Additionally, any content you upload (photos, documents) and usage data (e.g., IP address, cookies) may be collected to provide and improve our services.</p>

    <h3 class="small">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>Your data is used to operate and improve our website, provide the services you request, communicate with you, ensure security, and store uploaded content safely.</p>

    <h3 class="small">3. Cookies and Local Storage</h3>
    <p>We use only essential cookies and local storage to keep you logged in and remember your preferences. No tracking or advertising cookies are used without your consent.</p>

    <h3 class="small">4. Data Sharing</h3>
    <p>We do not share your personal data with third parties except when required by law or with your explicit consent.</p>

    <h3 class="small">5. Data Retention</h3>
    <p>Your data and uploaded content are stored only as long as necessary. You can request deletion of your personal data at any time.</p>

    <h3 class="small">6. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To exercise your rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@mywebsite.com">privacy@mywebsite.com</a>.</p>

    <h3 class="small">7. Security</h3>
    <p>We use reasonable measures to protect your data, but no system is completely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h3 class="small">8. Updates to This Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>
</div>

